data.description: Welcome home!  Lovely 2 level spacious rambler home ready to move in. UPPER level consists of a welcoming porch entryway that leads to the formal entrance, living room, dining room, country style kitchen filled with natural sunlight, 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms. The master bedroom offers a half bath and the other 2 rooms share a hallway bathroom. One can also access the rear deck from this main level where one can appreciate the mature trees and lawn areas. The LOWER level offers an oversized family room that can be subdivided and a bonus room created if needed, otherwise redesign it to your liking. This level also has the laundry room and access to the rear yard. OTHER highlights includes; newer plank flooring upstairs, new carpets in the lower level, HVAC system replaced 2020 and freshly painted.
